# Local runtime data directory at the repo root: ChromaDB index, Exploit-DB
# CSV cache, raw dumps. Leading slash anchors the rule to the repo root, so
# it does NOT match src/sec_recon_agent/mcp_server/data/ (which ships the
# MITRE ATT&CK mapping as part of the Python package and must be tracked).
/data/
*.db
*.sqlite

.aider*

# Frontend Node artifacts. node_modules is host-specific and large;
# .next is the local build cache. package-lock.json IS tracked so CI
# and the Dockerfile can use `npm ci` for deterministic installs.
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/.next/
frontend/out/

# CLAUDE.md is personal AI-tooling config; the global gitignore already
# excludes it. Do NOT add a `!CLAUDE.md` override here. Keep it local-only.
